{
  "text": "The 10 dimensional part shrinks when x + \u2192 \u2212\u221e, thus there is a null singularity a finite distance away in terms of the affine parameter. It is argued in [CITATION_1] that the matrix model works for this background with a time dependent action, where the matrix time t is chosen to coincide with x + .",
